"click on the &nbsp;<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"system-run.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"<guibutton>New Macro...</guibutton> button on the toolbar. A wizard will "
